Next Steps for Leadership
1.	Validate findings with department chiefs and operations managers.
2.	Pilot workload balancing in one high volume department.
3.	Deploy continuity focused scheduling for chronic care patients.
4.	Build the operational dashboard in Power BI or Tableau.
5.	Review impact after 60–90 days and refine staffing models.
